  • public class Sphere
extends ThreeDimensionalShapes
    The Sphere class extends the ThreeDimensionalShapes. The fields that are specific to this Sphere class radius, volume, and area. The methods that are specific to this class is the setters and getters for the instance fields, calculateArea function, and calculateVolume function which the area the perimeter respectively given a radius.
